Dialogue: 1,1:52:58.75,1:53:10.64,Howl_Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{holds the promise of love from the beginning of time}
Dialogue: 1,1:53:12.51,1:53:25.32,Howl_Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{even though I'm alone now with our yesterdays}
Dialogue: 1,1:53:25.94,1:53:32.03,Howl_Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{this day is born aglow}
Dialogue: 1,1:53:32.49,1:53:39.62,Howl_Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{like the first time we spoke}
Dialogue: 1,1:53:40.01,1:53:52.53,Howl_Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{somehow I lost you among all my memories}
Dialogue: 1,1:53:53.55,1:54:06.86,Howl_Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{you brush past my face softly as the breeze}
Dialogue: 1,1:54:39.31,1:54:51.70,Howl_Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{though we slipped apart like sunlight through the leaves}
Dialogue: 1,1:54:53.08,1:55:05.21,Howl_Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{the promise of love will live on eternally}
Dialogue: 1,1:55:06.50,1:55:19.18,Howl_Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{even though I'm alone now, my tomorrows are boundless}
